{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_01_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 零細なりの仕事",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、こっちが交通費リスト、こっちが領収書で……\nあ、あとグッズの件の手配もしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ here's the transportation expense list‚ and here are the receipts…\nOh‚ and I also need to arrange the merchandise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3366.6666666999995,
          "startTime": 9.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.333333299999,
          "startTime": 9.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "まだ誰か残ってるの？　……って\nなんだ、{user}さんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is someone still here?…\nOh‚ it's {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな夜遅くに一人こそこそ事務仕事なんて\n実は赤字経営で、帳簿を書き換えてたとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sneaking around doing office work so late at night…\nWere you secretly rewriting the books because of the deficit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしませんよ！\n今月の経費精算しないといけないのを、後回しにしてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn't do such a thing!\nI just postponed the expense settlement for this month and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、大変ですね\nそんな仕事、経理スタッフに任せればいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ sounds tough.\nYou should leave that kind of work to the accounting staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに人を雇うほどの余裕もない訳ね\nいかにも零細事務所って感じですね、まぁお気の毒",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have the luxury to hire so many people‚ right?\nIt really feels like a small office… Well‚ how unfortunate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.333333300003,
          "startTime": 46.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000,
          "startTime": 49
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9766.666666699997,
          "startTime": 51.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテみたいな大手と比べないで下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't compare us to major companies like Pret-a-Porter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざ零細を選んで就職したのはあなたでしょ\n……それ、全部入力するんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the one who chose to work for a small office‚ right?\n…Are you going to enter all of these?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ三分の一も終わってないように見えますけど\n本当に今日中に終わるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like you haven't even finished one-third of it.\nCan you really finish it today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.062505800007,
          "startTime": 64.1663958391
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……頑張ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I'll do my best…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3933.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 68.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……ああもう、見てるだけでイライラする！！\nなんでキーボード打つだけでそんなトロいのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh‚ just watching you type makes me irritated!!\nWhy are you so slow just typing on the keyboard?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとそこの席、私にかわって下さい！\nその領収書を一通り入力すればいいんでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you there‚ switch seats with me!\nYou just need to input those receipts‚ right?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "交通費はもう入ってるから……こっちの領収書ね\n衣装代がこれとこれで……ちょっとこれ先々月のですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The transportation expenses are already included… I mean these receipts here.\nThe costume expenses are these… oh‚ wait‚ this one is from two months ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 79.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1233.3333333000098,
          "startTime": 81.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2700.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 82.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.0000000000114,
          "startTime": 83.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_keytap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.666666600014,
          "startTime": 85.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "……星見プロ、放漫経営なんじゃありません？\nこの規模のオフィスにしては電気代かかり過ぎです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Isn't Hoshimi Production running a loose financial ship?\nThe electricity bill is too high for an office of this size.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "備品に、お茶代にお菓子代もやたらかかってるし……\nどうせ安物のお茶しか置いてないくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The office supplies‚ tea‚ and snack expenses are excessive too…\nEven though they only provide cheap tea…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "どうせならここの事務所の会計データはないんですか？\nほら、私も今は星見プロの所属な訳ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you have any accounting data for this office?\nWell‚ I'm affiliated with Hoshimi Production now‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、さすがにそこまでは見せられませんからね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I can't show you that much‚ of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、残念\nうまいこと、ここの経営乗っ取れないかと思ったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ what a pity.\nI thought maybe I could take over the management of this office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……それにしても、トップアイドルともなると\n経理にも強くなるものなんですかね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Anyway‚ when you become a top idol‚\ndo you also become skilled in accounting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "……別に、そういうことはないと思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't think that's the case.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスを結成する前、アパレルをやっていた時に\n必要になって覚えただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I learned it out of necessity\nwhen I was doing apparel before forming IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……言われてみれば確かに資料にそんなことも\n『ERFOLG』ってブランドでしたっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… now that you mention it‚ the documents did mention that…\nIt was the brand called 'ERFOLG‚' right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、それです\nあまり人を頼れなかったので、自分でやるしかなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's right.\nSince I couldn't rely on others much‚ I had to do it myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、テナント料とか材料の仕入れ値とか人件費とか\nやってみたら、予想外の部分で凄くお金がかかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I started handling things like rent‚ material costs‚ and labor costs‚\nI realized it cost a lot more than I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "結局、服のデザインやっているより\nお金を管理してる時間の方がずっと長かったんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ I spent more time managing money\nthan designing clothes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今月分の入力終わりましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'm done with this month's input.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "来月からは、領収書をこうなるまで溜め込まずに\nマメに整理することをお勧めします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From next month‚ I recommend you organize receipts promptly\nwithout letting them pile up like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、失礼しま……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ if you'll excuse me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、franさん、ちょっと待って下さい\n折り入って頼みたいことが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ fran-san‚ please wait a moment.\nThere's something I'd like to request…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか？\n言っておきますけど、面倒な仕事はごめんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it?\nJust so you know‚ I don't like troublesome tasks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……今度のライブの物販で、スリクスのグッズも\nラインナップに入れようと思ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I was thinking of including IIIX merchandise\nin the sales at the next live concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そのデザインをfranさんにお願いしたいんです\nアパレルの経験もあるし適任だと思いまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to ask you to design the merchandise.\nYou have experience in apparel‚ after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "なーんだ、グッズですか\n新衣装を作らせてくれるなら、喜んでやったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see… Merchandise.\nI would have gladly done it if you had asked me to create new costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "はは、予算がなくてすみません……\n今のところ、キーホルダーなんかを考えてるんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ sorry‚ we don't have the budget for that…\nFor now‚ I'm thinking of keychains or something like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor024.m4a",
      "text": "ふん、仕方ないですね\n零細事務所で、他に人もいないようですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph‚ I guess that can't be helped.\nSince there's no one else in this small office‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor025.m4a",
      "text": "……でもグッズも一度やってみたかったのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But I've always wanted to try making merchandise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-kor026.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、こんな零細事務所なんてって思ってたけど\n零細には零細なりの仕事ってあるものですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it seems there are different kinds of work\neven in a small business like this!",
        "id": ""
