      "text": "スリクスは、完璧なステージとビジュアルの華やかさで\n若い女性に凄く人気がありますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX has a great following among young women\ndue to your perfect stage performances and visuals‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "でも俺は、もうちょっと下の……背伸びしたい年頃の\n女の子達にもアピールしたいと思ってまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I also want to appeal to younger girls\nwho aspire to be like you…",
