      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……多分、そこの尖った部分を丸めれば\n問題はなくなると思うんですけど",
